CopyArrivalDate yes

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Host posteo.de
Port 143
User male.schmitt@posteo.de
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.config/mail/posteo_pass.gpg"
SSLType STARTTLS

MaildirStore posteo-local
Subfolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/.mail/posteo/Inbox

Channel posteo
Master :posteo-remote:
Slave :posteo-local:
Pattern *
Create Both
SyncState *

IMAPStore uni-remote
Host imap.kit.edu
Port 993
User uydvo@student.kit.edu
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.config/mail/uni_pass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMech LOGIN

MaildirStore uni-local
Subfolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.mail/uni/
Inbox ~/.mail/uni/Inbox

Channel uni
Master :uni-remote:
Slave :uni-local:
Pattern *
Create Both
SyncState *
